 I saw this happen once, and the bus needed a new ignition switch.  it was 
crossing inside the switch where it shouldn't have.

a good ignition switch fixed the problem.

You could alwways pull the wires off the switch and hot wire the bus.   It 
that gives no smoke, i'd think it was the switch
